sequenceDiagram
    actor User as Developer<br>(Phone)
    participant TG as Telegram API
    participant BOT as ralph-telegram<br>(teloxide)
    participant STATE as Bot State<br>telegram-state.json
    participant BUS as Event Bus
    participant EL as Event Loop<br>(Primary Loop)
    participant AGENT as AI Agent<br>(Claude/Kiro/Gemini)

    Note over User,AGENT: Human-to-Agent: /build command

    User->>TG: /build feature-auth
    TG->>BOT: Update received
    BOT->>STATE: Store chat_id, command
    BOT->>BUS: Publish human.guidance
    BUS->>EL: Guidance event queued

    EL->>EL: Squash guidance into<br>numbered ROBOT GUIDANCE list
    EL->>AGENT: Execute with hat + guidance injected

    AGENT->>AGENT: Plan, implement, iterate

    Note over AGENT,User: Agent-to-Human: human.interact (blocks loop)

    AGENT->>BUS: Emit human.interact<br>("Auth strategy: JWT or session cookies?")
    BUS->>EL: Interaction event
    EL->>EL: Block event loop
    EL->>BOT: Forward question to human
    BOT->>TG: sendMessage(chat_id, question)
    TG->>User: Display question on phone

    Note over User: Developer considers and replies

    User->>TG: "Use JWT with refresh tokens"
    TG->>BOT: Update received
    BOT->>STATE: Match reply to pending interaction
    BOT->>BUS: Publish human.response
    BUS->>EL: Response event
    EL->>EL: Unblock event loop (timeout was 300s)

    EL->>AGENT: Continue with human response

    AGENT->>AGENT: Complete implementation
    AGENT->>BUS: Emit code.complete

    Note over User,AGENT: Status Check: /status command

    User->>TG: /status
    TG->>BOT: Update received
    BOT->>EL: Query loop state
    EL-->>BOT: iteration: 12, hat: reviewer,<br>tasks: 3/5 complete
    BOT->>TG: sendMessage(chat_id, status report)
    TG->>User: Display formatted status

    Note over User,AGENT: Approval: /approve command

    User->>TG: /approve merge loop-007
    TG->>BOT: Update received
    BOT->>BUS: Publish human.guidance<br>("approve merge loop-007")
    BUS->>EL: Process merge approval

    Note over BOT: Send failures: 3 retries<br>with exponential backoff.<br>Timeout (300s) resumes loop<br>if human does not respond.
